  "3033520": {
    "name": "OYASUMII",
    "steam_appid": 3033520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/17e99cffdba76b4fe762f83b6b152405.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>探索复古旅行的怀旧情怀</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到OYASUMII，我们的恐怖与探索之宝，灵感来自PSX和N64时代的经典作品。沉浸在一个独特的体验中，在这个旅程中，怀旧与恐怖交织，在边界空间和扭曲世界中穿行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/7b44d15ac291a8a59bdb74df7f1e9621.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/7b44d15ac291a8a59bdb74df7f1e9621.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/7b44d15ac291a8a59bdb74df7f1e9621.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>沉浸在 DREAM QUEST ONLINE 线上宇宙</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在由NEO PROJECT团队开发的OYASUMII中，你将踏上充满神秘与危险的旅程，进入梦境探索在线的边界。在这个唤起最受喜爱的复古游戏的虚拟现实中，你将行走在超现实的景观中，面对挑战逻辑的恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/c46530ac4d5451530d7b56221f25ecbc.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/c46530ac4d5451530d7b56221f25ecbc.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/c46530ac4d5451530d7b56221f25ecbc.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>揭开这个扭曲世界的谜团</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索这个扭曲世界的黑暗秘密时，勇敢踏入那些专为迷惑和惊吓你而设计的迷宫。沉浸在OYASUMII独特的氛围中，每个角落都隐藏着意想不到的危险，每扇门都可能将你引向救赎，或是疯狂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/96ed33e3dbe33c9e0471ff30ca0c540e.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/96ed33e3dbe33c9e0471ff30ca0c540e.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/96ed33e3dbe33c9e0471ff30ca0c540e.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>¡跳跃，潜水和奔跑！</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏机制，你将悠闲地走过边界空间，跳跃以超越平台，奔跑以躲避潜伏的威胁。OYASUMII提供了一种挑战你的技能和理智的恐怖与探索体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/929c1763478c6ed3215b0f522602d37f.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>重温复古游戏的黄金时代</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借唤起复古游戏黄金时代的图形和配乐，OYASUMII将你带入一个充满怀旧和激动的世界。准备好迎接一场独特的冒险，它将把你的恐惧推向极限，并挑战你探索未知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.poster.avif?t=1748553992\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.webm?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033520/extras/fd1abf000bd4cd514f79603a2f02f74c.mp4?t=1748553992\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>准备好迎接难忘的冒险</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好了吗？揭开 OYASUMII 隐藏的秘密，逃离潜伏在梦境网络中的恐怖吧！加入这场独特的体验，准备好迎接一场永生难忘的冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>We want to thank @fubarmoe for their incredible work on the cover!</u></strong></p>",
